title: 1 BR 1 Bath Hopkins Condo
posting_body: ['Large 660 sf 1 Bedroom Condo Apartment for Rent in Hopkins located on quiet cul-de-sac on the 1st Floor.', 'It has 1 Full Bathroom, Kitchen, Living Room, Dining Room, Patio, lots of closet space, Air Conditioner, Garbage Disposal, Refrigerator, Dishwasher, Range.', 'Unit has Storage Locker.', 'You can park your car in the large Parking Lot.', 'Laundry Room on the same Floor.', 'This condo is minutes from downtown Hopkins and Excelsior Boulevard.', 'There are many local restaurants, bakeries, and shopping along 11th Avenue.', 'The unit is close to parks, bike paths, public gardens and walking areas.', 'Close to Edina, St Louis Park, Minnetonka, and Eden Prairie - Near Bus line', 'Address:                  930 6th St S #1, Hopkins, MN. 55343', 'Restrictions: \t\tNo Pets.', 'Requirements:        No Prior Evictions, No Prior Convictions.', 'Fees:\t\t\t$50 Application Fee per Person - non refundable for background check', 'Security Deposit:\t$1295', 'Rent:                       $1295 per month', 'Section 8:               YES - we do take Section 8', 'Utilities: \t\tTenant pays for Electric, TV, Phone, Internet.', 'Landlord pays for All other utilities and Association Dues.', 'Available for rent September 1st 2022.', 'Minimum 1 Year Lease.', 'Please email or text', 'show contact info', 'for more info.', 'Search: Apartment, apt, 1br, 1 br 1 bedroom.', '1 bedrooms, condo, one bedroom']
